e-date=2 June 2015 |access-date=20 August 2017 |df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"metaphor\">{{Cite web |url=http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/news/features/it-took-aamir-khan-to-go-and-convince-anil-kapoor-for-dil-dhadakne-do-zoya-akhtar/ |title=\"It took Aamir Khan to go and convince Anil Kapoor for Dil Dhadakne Do\" \u2013 Zoya Akhtar |last=Jha, Subhash K. |date=1 June 2015 |publisher=Bollywood Hungama |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170821004536/http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/news/features/it-took-aamir-khan-to-go-and-convince-anil-kapoor-for-dil-dhadakne-do-zoya-akhtar/ |archive-date=21 August 2017 |access-date=20 August 2017 |df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"mother\">{{Cite web |url=http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/raveena-tandon-ranveer-singh-dil-dhadakane-do-zoya-akhtar/1/361800.html |title=When Raveena Tandon refused to play Ranveer Singh's mother |date=14 May 2014 |website=India Today |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140517030656/http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/raveena-tandon-ranveer-singh-dil-dhadakane-do-zoya-akhtar/1/361800.html |archive-date=17 May 2014 |access-date=31 May 2014 |df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"convince\">{{Cite web |url=http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/news/features/it-took-aamir-khan-to-go-and-convince-anil-kapoor-for-dil-dhadakne-do-zoya-akhtar/ |title=\"It took Aamir Khan to go and convince Anil Kapoor for Dil Dhadakne Do\" \u2013 Zoya Akhtar |last=Jha, Subhash K. |date=1 June 2015 |publisher=Bollywood Hungama |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170821004536/http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/news/features/it-took-aamir-khan-to-go-and-convince-anil-kapoor-for-dil-dhadakne-do-zoya-akhtar/ |archive-date=21 August 2017 |access-date=27 August 2017}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"manipulative\">{{Cite web |url=https://www.thenational.ae/arts-culture/anil-kapoor-on-playing-a-manipulative-patriarch-in-dil-dhadakne-do-1.105956 |title=Anil Kapoor on playing a manipulative patriarch in Dil Dhadakne Do |last=Khan, Ujala Ali |date=2 Jun 2015 |website=[[The National (Abu Dhabi)|The National]] |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170828010613/https://www.thenational.ae/arts-culture/anil-kapoor-on-playing-a-manipulative-patriarch-in-dil-dhadakne-do-1.105956 |archive-date=28 August 2017 |access-date=27 August 2017 |df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"amother\">{{Cite web |url=http://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/bollywood/shefali-shah-i-was-21-when-i-played-a-mother/ |title=Shefali Shah: I was 21 when I played a mother |last=Ghosh, Sankhayan |date=13 June 2015 |website=The Indian Express |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170827172422/http://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/bollywood/shefali-shah-i-was-21-when-i-played-a-mother/ |archive-date=27 August 2017 |access-date=27 August 2017 |df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"screen\">{{Cite web |url=http://www.rediff.com/movies/report/i-hate-myself-on-screen/20150604.htm |title=I hate myself on screen |last=N, Patcy |date=4 June 2015 |publisher=[[Rediff.com]] |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170827171406/http://www.rediff.com/movies/report/i-hate-myself-on-screen/20150604.htm |archive-date=27 August 2017 |access-date=27 August 2017 |df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"reveal\">{{Cite web |url=http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/ranveer-singh-dil-dhadakne-do-zoya-akhtar-turkey-interview-hurriyet/1/372526.html |title=Did Ranveer Singh reveal the plot of Dil Dhadakne Do? |date=15 July 2014 |website=India Today |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170829171510/http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/ranveer-singh-dil-dhadakne-do-zoya-akhtar-turkey-interview-hurriyet/1/372526.html |archive-date=29 August 2017 |access-date=27 August 2017 |df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"bts\">{{Cite web |url=http://daily.bhaskar.com/news/ENT-BOW-behind-the-scenes-what-happened-when-dil-dhadakne-do-ship-pullmantur-broke-down-5012393-PHO.html |title=Behind The Scenes: What happened when Dil Dhadakne Do ship Pullmantur broke down? |last=Kulkarni, Onkar |date=4 June 2015 |website=[[Dainik Bhaskar]] |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170829171509/http://daily.bhaskar.com/news/ENT-BOW-behind-the-scenes-what-happened-when-dil-dhadakne-do-ship-pullmantur-broke-down-5012393-PHO.html |archive-date=29 August 2017 |access-date=29 August 2017 |df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"filming\">{{Cite web |url=http://www.mid-day.com/articles/dil-dhadakne-do-cast-begin-shooting-in-mumbai/15538190 |title='Dil Dhadakne Do' cast begin shooting in Mumbai |date=18 August 2014 |website=[[Mid Day]] |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150106140122/http://www.mid-day.com/articles/dil-dhadakne-do-cast-begin-shooting-in-mumbai/15538190 |archive-date=6 January 2015 |access-date=29 August 2017 |df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"visual\">{{Cite web |url=http://www.dnaindia.com/entertainment/report-dil-dhadakne-do-was-logistically-insane-visually-gorgeous-and-emotionally-cathartic-zoya-akhtar-2086979 |title='Dil Dhadakne Do' was logistically insane, visually gorgeous and emotionally cathartic: Zoya Akhtar |date=18 May 2015 |website=[[Daily News and Analysis]] |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150723004416/http://www.dnaindia.com/entertainment/report-dil-dhadakne-do-was-logistically-insane-visually-gorgeous-and-emotionally-cathartic-zoya-akhtar-2086979 |archive-date=23 July 2015 |access-date=29 August 2017 |df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"facts\">{{Cite web |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hindi/bollywood/news/Some-interesting-facts-from-the-sets-of-Dil-Dhadakne-Do/articleshow/47573828.cms |title=Some interesting facts from the sets of 'Dil Dhadakne Do' |date=7 June 2015 |website=The Times of India |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161010162435/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hindi/bollywood/